msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I found her in one corner of an empty classroom.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>She was sitting in a chair, hands on her knees,\n"
"staring absently at the floor.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>She looked like maybe she was upset, or angry. Or,\n"
"no...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>...She didn't have any expression at all.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>There was nothing on her face that you could call\n"
"emotion.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It was as if her original mask had been stripped away.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid "S-Sayaka? Are you okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid "Yeah...I'm fine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0009"
msgid "Actually, no...how could I possibly be fine?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid "What did we do to end up like this...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid "Why are they doing such terrible things to us...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0012"
msgid "I want out! Let me out of here right now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid "Sayaka! Calm down!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>As she thrashed around, I grabbed her by the\n"
"shoulders.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0015"
msgid "...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0016"
msgid ""
"I understand. I know how you feel right now. When I\n"
"think what might have happened to my family..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0017"
msgid "But now more than ever we have to stay calm!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0018"
msgid ""
"This is exactly what they want. They *want* us to lose\n"
"our composure and stop thinking rationally."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0019"
msgid "Think about itâ€”those videos have to be fake!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0020"
msgid "Because if those things really had happened..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0021"
msgid ""
"...people out there would be in an uproar. Our\n"
"families, the police, everyone!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0022"
msgid "Right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0023"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0024"
msgid "So let's just calm down, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0025"
msgid "Otherwise, we've already lost."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0026"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I knew I was trying to convince myself just as much as\n"
"her.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0027"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I kept repeating those words to myself, to clear away\n"
"the images that had been burned into my brain.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0028"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Be calm, okay?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0029"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Just be calm...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0030"
msgid ""
"As long as we work together, I'm sure we can find some\n"
"way out of here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0031"
msgid "And help might even come before that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0032"
msgid ""
"But...what if there *isn't* a way out? What if help\n"
"*never* comes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0033"
msgid "I-If that happens..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0034"
msgid ""
"...then I'll get you out of here myself! No matter\n"
"what it takes!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0035"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>When I said that, I paused...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0036"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I had no idea what had come over me.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0037"
msgid "Sayaka...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0038"
msgid "Please...help me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0039"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Her voice was small and shaky.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0040"
msgid "Why...? Why is this happening to me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0041"
msgid ""
"To kill, or be killed... I just can't take this\n"
"anymore...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0042"
msgid "Sayaka..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0043"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0044"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Finally, she raised her face up from my chest.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0045"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>She looked at me with those big, wet eyes of hers.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0046"
msgid "Can I...can I believe what you said?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0047"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0048"
msgid "That you'll help me get out?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0049"
msgid "No matter what it takes...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0050"
msgid "A-Absolutely!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0051"
msgid ""
"Makoto... You're the only one I can trust. So\n"
"please..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0052"
msgid ""
"No matter what happens, please always be there for me.\n"
"I need you on my side..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0053"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0054"
msgid "O-Of course I'll be there for you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0055"
msgid "No matter what, I'm always on your side. I mean..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0056"
msgid "...you *are* my assistant, after all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0057"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0058"
msgid "Thank you, Makoto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0059"
msgid "Hearing you say that, I feel like I can keep going."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0060"
msgid ""
"I can get through this...as long as you're here with\n"
"me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0061"
msgid "Like you said, I'm your assistant."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0062"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>The smile I'd come to know so well returned to her\n"
"face.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0063"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It felt a little forced, but still...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0064"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It was a huge improvement over how she was before.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0065"
msgid "...It's standing up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0066"
msgid "Kyah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0067"
msgid "Makoto! It's standing up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0068"
msgid "*What's* standing up!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0069"
msgid "Do you even have to ask?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0070"
msgid "Your flagpole!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0071"
msgid "Get the hell out of here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0072"
msgid "No! No! I wanna join in!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0073"
msgid ""
"Dammit! Well if you won't leave, then tell us what the\n"
"hell is up with those videos!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0074"
msgid "Ahh...it's about to come out..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0075"
msgid "It's gonna come out! My pristine, pure white..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0076"
msgid "...stuffing!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0077"
msgid ""
"My honest, innocent stuffing is about to come gushing\n"
"out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0078"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I balled up my fist, took aim, and swung as hard as I\n"
"could.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0079"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I had never put so much energy into a single motion\n"
"before in my life.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0080"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I leaned back, channeling all my power, and let go\n"
"with everything I had...!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0081"
msgid "Guwah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0082"
msgid "A-Are you okay!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0083"
msgid ""
"If I hadn't avoided your punch, you would have just\n"
"violated school regulations."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0084"
msgid "But boy are you slow slow slow slow SLOW!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0085"
msgid ""
"I could've downed a thousand-dollar full-course dinner\n"
"in the time it took you to finish your swing!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0086"
msgid ""
"Your speed, agility, alertness, passion, boldness,\n"
"sense of despair, antagonization, it's all lacking!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0087"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0088"
msgid "What the heck was that just now...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0089"
msgid "He just wanted to mess with us..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0090"
msgid "Well, for now...you wanna just head back?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0091"
msgid "Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0092"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Monokuma had come along and swiftly destroyed the good\n"
"mood we'd just created.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0093"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Sayaka and I headed back to the dorms.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0094"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>This is one of the monitors Monokuma appears on.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0095"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I don't have time to worry about that right now!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0096"
msgid "Urgh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0097"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>A surveillance camera... And whoever's putting us all\n"
"through this must be on the other side of it...!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0098"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Who cares what time it is right now!?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0099"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Dammit! Thanks to this stupid piece of metal...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0100"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Isn't there anything we can do about it!?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0101"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Dammit! Thanks to this stupid piece of metal...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0102"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Isn't there anything we can do about it!?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0103"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>That's the desk I woke up on the day I got here...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0104"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>But that doesn't matter now!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0105"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I came here to see Sayaka. What's the point of leaving\n"
"now...!?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0106"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I came here to see Sayaka. What's the point of leaving\n"
"now...!?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
